byline.contributor: Ibrahim Sawab contributed reporting from Maiduguri, Nigeria.

lead_paragraph: The number killed in an errant bombing by a Nigerian military fighter jet on Tuesday included at least nine aid workers, humanitarian groups said Wednesday.
